derivation.yuyuan_name: late 16th cent.: from medieval Latin nonentitas 'non-existence'

entry.def: If you refer to someone as a nonentity, you mean that they are not special or important in any way.

example.ex: Amidst the current bunch of nonentities, he is a towering figure...
